OL,5,G1820 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FIt's feedback time as the B&Bers
OL,7,     Fmeet to complain about breakfast
OL,8,     Feggs, dirty rooms and sleepless
OL,9,     Fnights. One owner's strategy comes
OL,10,     Funder scrutiny, before the winner
OL,11,     Fis announced.
OL,12,G1850 Location, Location, Location
OL,13,     FKirstie and Phil help Brett and
OL,14,     FJo, and first-time buyers Ben and
OL,15,     FPip, scour the competitive
OL,16,     Fproperty market in Nottingham,
OL,17,     Fwhere trendy homes in the right
OL,18,     Fspot are scarce.
